  <h2>A Byte of Python</h2>
  <p>This is a book on programming using the Python language. It serves as a tutorial or guide to the Python language for a beginner audience. If all you know about computers is how to save text files, then this is the book for you.</p>
  <p><a title="Read Online" href="/notes/python/">⇒ Read Online</a></p>
