  <h2>A Byte of Vim</h2>

  <p>A Byte of Vim is a guide to help you to learn to learn about Vim, the text editor of choice for many programmers. This guide is aimed at both beginners who do not know anything about vi or vim and wish to learn how to become more productive in their writing, and intermediate users who wish to pick up advanced Vim tricks.</p>
  <p><a title="Read Online" href="/notes/vim/">⇒ Read Online</a></p>
